metadata.description: The App uses an insecure Random Number Generator.

playstore_details.title: Pedometer App - Step Counter
playstore_details.description:
Pedometer App - Step Counter, a free & accurate step tracker to track your daily steps, walking distance, time and burned calories.

This personal step counter features clear daily, weekly, and monthly charts so you can see your activity data at a glance. It works on all Android devices, using sensors instead of GPS for accurate step counting, which makes it more private and supports offline use.

✨ Why choose Pedometer App - Step Counter?
✦ Free & easy to use
✦ Accurate step counting
✦ 100% private 
✦ Detailed activity data charts
✦ One-click share walking reports
✦ Handy screen widgets
✦ Available offline
✦ No GPS tracking
✦ Work on all Android devices
✦ Colorful themes

❤️ Easy-to-use Step Counter
No wearable device required, just put your phone in your pocket, bag, or hold it in hand to auto start counting steps. It uses sensors instead of GPS to track steps, saving a lot of battery.

🚶 Accurate Step Tracker
Adjust sensor sensitivity to ensure more accurate step counting. Even if the screen is locked or there is no network connection, all steps will be automatically counted to live up to your every step.

📝 Manually Edit Steps
You can manually edit the number of steps by time period to reflect your actual exercise situation. No more worries about losing your step records!

📊 Activity Data Analysis
Get insights into your activity levels with detailed graphs showing steps, walking time, distance, and calories burned. You can view data by day, week or month, and understand your most active times and exercise trends.

📱 Handy Screen Widgets
Easily add widgets to your home screen to track your daily steps without entering the app. You can also customize the size or style of widgets according to your preference.

🎨 Personalized Themes
Colorful themes are available for you to choose from: fresh lawn green, quiet lake blue, vibrant sunshine yellow... You can customize it to your liking, adding color and vitality to your walking journey.

👤 100% Private
Your privacy matters. We don't collect any of your personal data or share your data with other third parties.

Features coming soon:
🥛 Water tracker - Remind you to drink water on time;
📉 Weight tracker - Record and follow your weight changes;
🏅Achievements - Unlock badges as you reach different fitness levels;
🎾 Personalized activities - Track training data for various sports;
🗺️ Workout map - Visualize your activity routes;
☁️ Data backup - Sync your health data to Google Drive.

⚙️ Permissions required:
- Notification permission is required to send you reminders;
- Physical activity permission is required to calculate your step data;
- Storage permission is required to store step data on your device. 

Step Counter - Pedometer App is not only a walk tracker, but also a leader in healthy living. This pedometer free & versatile fitness tracker accurately records your fitness efforts, providing detailed insights into your activity levels. Whether you're looking for a walk tracker, distance tracker to monitor your daily activity or a comprehensive fitness tracker to analyze your health data, Step Tracker has you covered. Just try this steps app now!

We value your feedback and suggestions! If you have any questions or ideas, please feel free to contact us at stepappfeedback@gmail.com. Let's embark on this fitness journey together!

android.permission.ACTIVITY_RECOGNITION (dangerous): allow application to recognize physical activity - Allows an application to recognize physical activity.

android.permission.POST_NOTIFICATIONS (dangerous): allows an app to post notifications. - Allows an app to post notifications
